title: how it works
pid: c38f892c-efa8-4f8f-aaac-77447afca444
body: |2-
  #+BEGIN_SRC haskell
  -- compare:
  p1 = sound "[feel*2 feel:3, hc:3 hc:2 hc:4 ho:1]"

  d1 $        p1
  d1 $ brak $ p1
  d1 $ cat $ [ p1, -- another way to say `brak`
               early (1/4) $ fastcat [silence, p1] ]
  #+END_SRC
